latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Vit. C Rich Routine with @purebypriyanka 💛

It’s been a while since I’ve been using these 3 products easily 3-4 months now and I absolutely LOVE them! 🙌🏼 

💛 The Vit C face wash is extremely gentle and doesn’t rip the skin off moisture or natural oils. It’s the perfect addition to an anti-pigmentation skincare routine. 💯 

💛 The clay based Vit C face mask is so gentle and does what it claims! It helps to even out skin texture and skin tone soooo well. It also reduces acne inflammation ever so slightly :) (since it’s clay based use it only once a week and wash within 10-12 mins of application)

💛 Swarnprabha facial oil is a powerhouse of ingredients! It is super effective, so lightweight and smells heavenly. The rich ingredients help to calm inflammation, reduce acne marks and reduce hyper pigmentation slowly with regular use. This is easily one of my favorite oils!

Have you used any of these products? What was your experience like? 🤓
